metadata.name: The Notorious B.I.G
metadata.description:
Biggie Smalls, commonly known as "The Notorious B.I.G.," was a well-known hip-hop artist and the face of gangsta rap on the East Coast. Since I was eleven years old, I've been listening to rap/hip-hop music. Biggie songs still make me bop my head whenever I hear them. My art is highly influenced by classic hip-hop artists such as The Notorious B.I.G.
